Title: Wizards' Rui Hachimura: Puts up 15 and six in win
Description: Hachimura had 15 points (6-8 FG, 1-2 3Pt, 2-3 FT), six rebounds and one steal in Monday's overtime win over the Lakers. The Wizards erased a double-digit second-half deficit, and Hachimura hit some key shots down the stretch to help Washington to its fifth straight victory.
Author: CBSSports.com
